Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.02,0:00:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗体已经送达了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我很想和克洛维斯说话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:18.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要尽快执行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个计划
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.31,0:01:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 6
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}被夺走的假面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:02:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看 为什么会在这里 是嫌疑犯吧  克洛维斯殿下那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师说是抓错人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过肯定是因为有可疑之处才会被抓的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是恐怖分子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒不会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校至少会确认一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是名誉布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 没有区别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能只是害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.06,0:02:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要和他说说话就知道是怎么样的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行动力过于旺盛了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经七年没用过了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:02:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:02:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"去屋顶说话"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事 我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事都是多亏了你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒是你 如果不是为了保护我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:11.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是把欠你的还给你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.22,0:03:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在密封舱里的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗时很混乱 我们失散了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你那边 没有她的消息吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎除了亲卫队以外谁也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于名字… 还是叫你鲁鲁修吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的我 在记录中已经是死了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修·兰佩鲁基
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在用的是这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军事法庭那边怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有怎么转来这里上学…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.73,0:03:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也吓了一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到鲁鲁修居然也在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了搜查能够顺利进行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某人作了这样的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那个人还说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17岁的话就应该好好上学…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些全都是克洛维斯皇兄画的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温柔的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是皇兄呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功引出了游击队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推测其根据地的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时向上汇报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…  柯内莉娅!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旧时代的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达尔顿  就是在这里面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[安德列·达尔顿 Andres Darlton]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  您打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种战力差距 没必要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降吧  愚蠢的ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的布里塔尼亚混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.57,0:05:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来ZERO不在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐个扫荡也真是没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就在这里腐烂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  娜娜莉  咲世子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我有礼物要送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这双手…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然… 平安无事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了  娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 今晚能留下吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀已经是这个学校的学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以随时都可以见面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为还有军队的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也不是说每天都行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还打算继续做军人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被调到技术部了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再那么危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技术部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好坐着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和七年前不同  今天我是主人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像变得稳重了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你则是变得爽快了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:06:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是让你在房间待着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在新宿遇到的布里塔尼亚军人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他的话 不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是… 我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来  杰雷米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尔弗德卿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[吉尔伯特·G.P.·吉尔弗德 Gilbert G.P. Guilford]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于查清楚了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是排除了关于谋反的嫌疑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ORANGE君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你们纯血派放走了ZERO的事实却不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,官降三级
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有两个选择
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要么从一个初级机师重新开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要么回乡下去种ORANGE吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉也会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在学校还是装作不认识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么解释
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和名誉布里塔尼亚人是朋友什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄不好还会暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是皇子这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再给你们添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前你也是这样  尽是只考虑别人的情况…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得  很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到我还会有说这句话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 你昨天好像有点奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没在学生会露脸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界史考试没考好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是这样的说辞…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然新闻还没有报道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但"武士之血"已被柯内莉娅剿灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们可是中部最大的组织啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却在一瞬间…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说ZERO  我们再这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要着急
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等待时机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我会联系你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个喜欢缠人的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该和他们断绝联系了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[滚回…贫民区]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 吵到你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么没去学校?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 不知怎么… 总觉得…好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们班里来了个转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是杀害克洛维斯殿下的嫌疑犯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙多次惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,签收的是男子的名字 没问题吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把假面藏在这里面吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Geass不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西可是能成为铁证的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  我泡了茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦  这个香味… 又是披萨?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在攒必胜客积分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近有没有变得软绵绵的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[意指吃必胜客吃到虚胖哦~虚胖~]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说上臂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不准碰哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在想会不会发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀被人欺负了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事 是需要时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能想想其他办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住! 还给我!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.84,0:11:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能被一只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被区区一只猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能因为这么白痴的事而暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没有碰哦  嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:11:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什么很重要的东西被猫叼走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重要的东西是指?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但肯定是非常重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 哥哥那种惊慌失措的惨叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次听到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修的很重要的东西究竟是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情书?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尴尬的相片?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写情诗的小册子?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情诗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我们身上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对会在鲁鲁修之前抢回来给你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他之前!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这时候那些恐怖分子在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能展开包围作战了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再加深她的疑心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难缠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢 我就这样说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只猫怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是那个假面吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个ZERO的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:12:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 在这种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我忘掉  刚才看到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是学生会会长米蕾·阿斯福德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在请立即去抓住在校内逃窜的猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社团活动全部暂停
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协力的社团可以享受经费预算的优待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 抓住猫咪的人还将获得超级幸运大奖!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是 学生会成员的吻!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会… 也就是说… 我的也算?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为学生会成员的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐的樱唇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会只吻下脸颊就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就算脸颊也满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 可以指定位置吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的初吻啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会会员的话 也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修也可以咯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望是米蕾姐姐比较好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在这种情况下做百合宣言啦 (Coming-Out)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,论机动力的话 我们占绝对优势
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快找木天蓼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[木天蓼：猫最喜欢的"草本兴奋剂",逗猫专用]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持就是胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉到猫的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它叼着的东西交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:18.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给…我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长… 只会多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然擅自把人当作奖品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说布里塔尼亚人啊  真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的 很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害 难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初不设定成病弱少女就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什么打扮啊  莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是关系到我们的吻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉 那只猫有什么特征吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想它的脚可能不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为脚步声稍微有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:14:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只猫是这么叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是悠闲的学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在明明还是服丧期呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个 这里的大学…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经和他们谈妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不用把Lancelot赶出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[注: NUMBERS是对被占领地人民的通称,比如日本为11]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说NUMBERS不行什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我们学生会的人抓到它的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能得到奖品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说吻的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也要认真地露一手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不准在校内飙车!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 我们的吻就安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后方就拜托莎莉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲打算对谁用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是对… 鲁鲁?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.24,0:16:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么会那样想?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…这个嘛…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来追猫咪?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你赶快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.71,0:16:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  学生会会长说要抓住它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了别管啦  你快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫就由我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动是我的强项啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次小鸟逃掉的时候也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别扯陈年旧事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过七年前而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是一如既往的体力白痴!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经追到了是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁找到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 不要怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧 交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前明明更加个人主义的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人 难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也过于安心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉 突然浑身脱力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:51.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修大危机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托转校生的福 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是上次那只猫嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.33,0:18:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 救了鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得不错啊 转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只猫 是不是叼着什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像戴着什么似的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不是看得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不知道什么时候就掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是有东西忘了 让我先走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:30.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的『尴尬的秘密』
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊 会长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为终于可以抓住你的弱点了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁太爱装帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 你们两个人是旧识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 和ELEVEN…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:18:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否让他加入学生会?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:05.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们学校规定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生一定要加入某个社团
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是副会长的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就算是一事平息了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位都把耳朵凑过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾承诺过的奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就由还是半个会员的我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将就下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 为了庆祝抓住猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是由新人请客
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别趁机敲诈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是莎莉 多多关照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是利瓦尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是学生会会长米蕾·阿斯福德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有请神圣布里塔尼亚帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第98代唯一皇帝陛下发言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人 是不平等的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生来就健行之人  美貌之人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母贫困之人  病弱之人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出生  成长  才能  所有人都是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人就是为了被差别对待而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以人类才会争斗  竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.83,0:21:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由此才产生了进化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.77,0:21:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不平等并非恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平等才有恶处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高呼权利平等的EU怎样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[EU：Europe Union，假想的欧洲同盟]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任期只是导致了众愚政治而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[任期制：同帝国继承制相反]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追求平等均富的中华联邦呢?  造就了一群懈怠的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我们布里塔尼亚并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.04,0:21:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,争斗  竞争  一直持续着在进化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进化? 真是个好词
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有布里塔尼亚在前进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着未来在前进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.41,0:21:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾子克洛维斯之死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是布里塔尼亚在持续进化的最佳证明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竞争  掠夺  获取  支配
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此尽头  有着未来!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:22:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Britannia…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.75,0:22:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修的敌人…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.88,0:23:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"否定"这个词都显得太温和
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.27,0:23:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.16,0:23:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个男人就是布里塔尼亚的象征的话 我就摧毁他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.43,0:23:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在这条路上 还有皇姐柯内莉娅阻挡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.16,0:23:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.35,0:24:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.40,0:24:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经拥有了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.49,0:24:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只身一人也能…
